  (:require [reagent.core :as r]

            [reagent-mui.material.button :refer [button]]

(defn add-file-to-ipfs [filename file-data]
  (let [blob (js/Blob. (clj->js [file-data]) #js {:type "image/*"})]
    (ifiles/add @file-data {:path filename}
                (fn [err files]
                  (println [err files])))))

(defn ipfsTest []
  (init-ipfs)
;;(init-ipfs {:host "http://127.0.0.1:5001" :endpoint "/api/v0"})

;;fls to avoid clashes with ls from files.ls

;;Files upload on NODEJS see files_test
;;Files upload -- reagent
  (let [f (atom nil)]
    (fn []
      [:form
       {:on-submit
        (fn [e]
          (.preventDefault e)
          (add-file-to-ipfs (.-name @f) @f))}
       [:input {:type "file"
                :on-change #(let [v (-> % .-target .-files (aget 0))]
                              (reset! f v))}]
       [:input
        {:type "submit"
         :value "Import"}]])))
